Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:12.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？等…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:13.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 伤口…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:22.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:25.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…你可还有伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:41.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都是罪业之子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这全都要怪你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:45.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好开心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:49.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能把我的心意传达给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这无从消解的怨恨啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:05.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了 鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:09.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的确丢下你逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也不该用这样的方式来报复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:14.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不该？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:19.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就算你这样做怨恨也不会消解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:31.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 这种程度确实完全无法消解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,骸很快就要复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:42.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以惩罚你们了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这回你们可别想跑了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:33.00,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}にじんでる歩道橋のらくがき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:44.22,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}置いてかれた自転車　誰かの帰りを待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:49.39,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}認めて　ただ存在を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.02,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕こそがオリジナル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.52,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あるいはそのレプリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.99,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕らの証明はどこにある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:03.83,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}人類の欠点は　見えもしないくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:09.08,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}愛とか絆とか信じられること
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:14.00,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕の罪はうたがったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.17,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}差し伸べられた君の右手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.13,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}初めて見たヒカリ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:29.18,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}僕らは———
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:33.00,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,岁月流转　天桥涂鸦终归消散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:44.22,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,静置难安　单车默待谁人与共还
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:49.39,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,坦然直面　存在世间　身外孑然一片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.02,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却难断　吾乃本源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.52,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,抑或水月云烟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.99,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,孰真孰幻　吾等安辩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:03.83,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,人心缺点难免　未曾得见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:09.08,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,爱与羁绊　却坚信依然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:14.00,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心疑难掩　吾罪何堪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.17,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,与君右手紧牵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.13,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,唯慨叹　光明初现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:29.18,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,吾等只盼……
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:48.49,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1029,1029)\pos(145,265)}第十七话\N无明之光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我真没想到你竟然会为我流泪呢 来夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…痛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还请你再温柔一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是傲娇里娇的那一面啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚抱着我的时候明明还那么温柔的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:15.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在进行数据连接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 须崎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:18.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:24.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,无明领域上空的自卫队侦察机捕捉到黑和朱的信号了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:25.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,银呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:30.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…仍然是毫无踪迹的沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:31.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…骸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,信号又中断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们适可而止不要太过接近无明领域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,侦察机放出紧急求救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,已前往厚木迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 这执念还真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是无可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:16.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:28.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这大概是焚毁珍贵样本的报应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也怪不得别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:34.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,十年啊 倒是没想到来得这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:42.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}粉灰に散るは　ほいがろん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,快让它住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,骸它在生气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我又怎么拦得住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志 你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:24.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志和笹目都深知自己罪业深重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以都不敢出手反抗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊…不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊…不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说是吧 艾米露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:51.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亚梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:12.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:17.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是我和笹目的罪业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:24.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 你们两个不只是把我丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,还从我身边抢走了赤司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:34.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,才把你从我身边抢走的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,很过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:44.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:45.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:58.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:01.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目才不会做那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就这样… 快跑吧赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,让你能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:34.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我对笹目的承诺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司 你这样怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没法自己从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这岂不是又要迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,等惩罚完这些坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,骸的怒火平息了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会把你抓回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,死神 得先找到死神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,进入无明领域？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:27.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 她让我留在这里支援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,须酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,能别当着外人叫这个名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这太危险了 就算你能挺过精神侵蚀的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那指挥车和驾驶服最多也只能坚持一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,再多的话你自己都有被尸钢化的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个小时啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是万一时的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在无论如何都要先确定里面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:56.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 可不要胡来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:01.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,最好把我们两个共联者也一起带上吧 须崎教官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,岩人 你的伤势如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:08.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,托这满怀爱意的包扎的福 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个电影院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,死神应该就在那附近才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:29.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司你在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点找到的话笹目她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:41.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想笹目她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想失去笹目啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司 快回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司…这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:11.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:27.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…当初大家一起玩的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:44.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么躲在这种地方啊 青司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕的话哭出来也不要紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,爱哭鬼皆志和只会撒娇的笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是跟在我身边就什么事都做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 确实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能想象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:26.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,被你背叛的我是怎样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你能想象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:34.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样呼唤都得不到回应的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:45.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目 皆志 我们一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他们要从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 笹目…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司 大家 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不要走呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:01.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:06.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司明明答应我要永远在一起的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把他带走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是都说了我们不能离开这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目 告诉我为什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:22.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要丢下我一个人…笹目…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会回来的吧 笹目 皆志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,会和赤司一起回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:44.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我被我的妹妹背叛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:50.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司…把赤司还给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:55.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦 我去接他就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:59.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司肯定也是想要和我在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人也一起带回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要大家都要好好接受惩罚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,骸 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但那时我震惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那时赤司的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他看我的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,让我明确地意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:26.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司他心中已经没有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:31.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 笹目 我那时的心情你能体会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你把赤司从我身边带走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司的心中已经不记得我的存在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 鸫 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,皆志你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:48.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么却要我来承受如此痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:06.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再让你们把赤司带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让笹目你把他抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,青司 现在我必须要倚仗你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:20.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样 我到底该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,脑海里一片混沌完全难明所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:27.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道我到底能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:32.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一点我现在很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:37.41,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}誰がために僕らは　未来を差し出さなきゃいけないんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:42.21,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}いつかじゃなく…今　教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:47.96,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}日常と非日常　あいだに川は流れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.88,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}迷いすべて　飲み込み
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:55.55,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}憧れは彼方　対岸のきらめき
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:59.02,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}The River Never Stops
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:12.24,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}不可侵な領域　仕舞い込んだ気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:17.08,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}あらわになる時に　人を傷つけ傷ついてく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:21.71,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}清くありたい　でもどうしようもない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.71,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}求めるままに　飢えてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.84,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}心を暗闇で埋めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:32.97,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}つながってたい　君に愛されたい　LA-LA-LA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:38.51,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}誰がために僕ら　二度と戻れない場所へ来たのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.39,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}理由を　訳を…問いかけても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:48.27,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}絶望と希望の　あいだに川は流れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:52.82,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}闇は何も　答えず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.16,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}気付けば夢さえ　対岸の泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.95,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}The River Never Stops
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:11.59,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}誰がために　朝日のぼり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:11.26,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an９}この街　静かに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:20.85,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}誰がために　星は降るのかを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:20.35,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an９}星は降るのだろう　ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.39,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}―――答えてみてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:28.23,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}本当は逃げ出したい　運命を振り切りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:37.66,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}そして僕たちは　どこへ行けば　いいの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:44.62,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}誰がために僕ら　二度と戻れない場所へ来たのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:49.00,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}理由を　訳を…問いかけても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:54.72,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}絶望と希望の　あいだに川は流れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:59.05,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}闇は何も　答えず
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.89,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}サヨナラを言うよ　対岸の純真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:05.81,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7}The River Never Stops
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:37.41,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}何人之故　须祭吾等明日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:42.21,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}莫待来日　相诉就在此时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:47.96,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}怒涛两隔　日常与非日常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.88,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}吾等迷茫　尽数汇聚流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:55.55,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}心中向往　对岸夺目光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:59.02,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}奔流不息　不为尧存桀亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:12.24,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}敞开心扉　抛却芥蒂阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:17.08,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}坦诚相见　却终互相伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:21.71,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}菩提镜台　怎奈俗世尘埃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.71,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}心有所念　欲火焚身难耐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.84,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}无尽黑暗　心已于此深埋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:32.97,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}愿可联络　只望得君怜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:38.51,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}何人之故　至此再难回头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.39,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}闻亦何苦　罔论借口理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:48.27,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}绝望希望　却隔怒涛如虬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:52.82,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}无尽黑暗　悄然默对所求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.16,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}南柯一梦　对岸云烟难留
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.95,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}抽足再入　已非前水奔流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:11.59,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}何人之故　朝阳无边喷薄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:11.26,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an9}足下街镇　声息皆无
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:20.85,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}何人之故　群星可将陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:20.35,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an9}群星终落　君意何如
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.39,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}心中迷惘　怎知是非对错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:28.23,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}奋力逃脱　挣脱命运掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:37.66,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}茫然四顾　何见吾等归所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:44.62,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}何人之故　至此再难回头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:49.00,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}闻亦何苦　罔论借口理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:54.72,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}绝望希望　却隔怒涛如虬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:59.05,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}无尽黑暗　悄然默对所求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.89,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}对岸纯真　挥别再不回眸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:05.81,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}抽足再入　已非前水奔流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是成为界联系统或是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:39.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不想失去笹目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的罪业到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家把我一个人丢下逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都是罪业之子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是罪业的话我也是一样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:19.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要怎样做你才能满足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想要我们怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:32.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的是你所期望的吗 鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也很悲伤吧 骸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这也无可奈何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再继续啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米露和笹目都已经受了那么多苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要对真亚梦出手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:22.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多也该告一段落去找赤司了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:30.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道赤司他…这种程度的联结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 机体竟如此轻盈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,简直比自己的手脚更自如
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:06.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉肯定没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:11.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样 应该是在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,轻易接近反而会拖后腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:34.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,骸才是要施予惩罚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能消去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:50.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这十年间所忍受的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,触碰不到任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有任何人可以沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在承受这无边的寂寞同时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:03.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是也忘却了那些还在注视着你的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,过去是无从消去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:07.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法将那伤痕累累的记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那自说自话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:13.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎样才能消去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,给不出答案就别在那信口雌黄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:30.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,和赤司一起…从这里离开？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们一起离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:39.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不能离开这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:42.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你不能永远留在这里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:43.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目她也一定是这样期望的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:56.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:03.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司 不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:20.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司和皆志 真亚梦也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,已接通和银的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 六个人都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:30.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:32.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,共信率…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:37.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然突破了理论上限？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 原来我们以前果然见过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是复仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能再早些…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:53.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,在创造出无明领域之前遇到大家的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:00.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,赤司 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是神木的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,无明领域里生长着大量的神木
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:13.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要带着这个就能不受无明领域的影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:17.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,鸫能一直平安也是拜它所赐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,神木…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:26.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但估计也只能生长在无明领域里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:39.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:43.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天和哥哥联结在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不知道该做什么 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:49.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,但心中怀着必须做点什么的念头就联结上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:53.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概哥哥他成为界联系统时也是这样的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,笹目你也是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:03.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会这样想也是受了你的影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是体会过那天的温暖才…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:15.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在彻底明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:17.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成为了界联系统
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你心中挂念的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不愿失去笹目你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:30.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我喜欢你啊 笹目
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.02,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You lose your mind, you crash
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:22:59.89,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A nervous breakdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:02.86,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You feel an urge inside, you crush
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.52,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no escape now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:07.69,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You try to change your life, you jump
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.45,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Another letdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.62,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But then you hear a voice inside
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:14.24,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You gotta open up your vision
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:15.87,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}See the life bestowed on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:18.08,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Blinded by reality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:20.62,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Broken ideology
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:23.13,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Heart in captivity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:24.00,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:25.30,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Exceeding the borders within
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.88,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seize your capability
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:30.34,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Endless possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.72,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Find your individuality
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.43,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Take pride, let the chase begin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:37.89,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me what direction you think I should take
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:39.35,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I know I'm gonna find the way』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:42.44,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me that this sable is for my own sake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:44.23,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『Hear what I've got to say』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:47.19,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me to believe the decisions you make
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:49.07,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}『I'm facing a new day』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:51.61,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So open up your blinded eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:54.07,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop living a lie and start living your life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:56.20,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.91,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today you're falling away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:00.79,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My way or no way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:03.83,OPED - jp,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today I'm breaking away
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.02,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,失汝心志　躯形难继
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:22:59.89,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,慌乱分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:02.86,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心潮涌动　冲荡破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.52,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,已是无路可退
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:07.69,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,逆天改命　奋力跃腾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.45,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,再落心灰意冷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.62,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,却闻心中轻语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:14.24,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,放眼茫然四顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:15.87,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,但见尘世夺予
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:18.08,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,现实毁盲双目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:20.62,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,仅余碎裂思悟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:23.13,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,心亦牢牢禁锢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:24.00,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,勿言轻弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:25.30,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,跨越心中束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.88,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,紧握汝力天成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:30.34,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,迸发无尽可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.72,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,寻汝真我个性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.43,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,昂首迈步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:37.89,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫要擅自定吾前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:39.35,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾定将自寻通途』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:42.44,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫言黑暗皆为吾敌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:44.23,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『但得静闻吾倾诉』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:47.19,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,莫诳吾从尔等好恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:49.07,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,『吾自面崭新朝暮』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:51.61,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,故舍犹豫再开盲眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:54.07,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,挣脱谎言自立世间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:56.20,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.91,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,此时汝却飘然离去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:00.79,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,足下再无别途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:03.83,OPED - chs,,0,0,0,,今日吾将突破禁锢
